                                        "p97"
                                    ], 
                                    "node_type": "appendix", 
                                    "text": "Section L. Settlement Charges. This section of the HUD-1A is similar to section L of the HUD-1, with minor changes or omissions, including deletion of lines 700 through 704, relating to real estate broker commissions. The instructions for section L in the HUD-1 should be followed insofar as possible. Inapplicable charges should be ignored, as should any instructions regarding seller items."
                                }, 
                                {
                                    "children": [], 
                                    "label": [
                                        "1024", 
                                        "A", 
                                        "h10", 
